author: The Linux Foundation
description:
🤲 A reminder that the most important skill in tech isn't the newest tool — it’s the commitment to keep learning!

Cyber Week makes that easier for everyone with up to 65% off certifications, bundles, subscriptions, courses, and cloud native learning paths.

Wherever you’re starting from, and however you communicate, your skills have a place in the open source community — and this week gives you the momentum to grow them.

Commit to learning in 2026, enroll today: https://hubs.la/Q03V4RL70

✳️ BONUS! Get a US$100 gift voucher to use for courses & certifications in 2026! 

#CyberWeek #CyberMonday #CloudNative #SysAdmin #DevOps #Engineer #Developers #Linux #ASL
title: The most important skill in tech isn't the newest tool — it’s the commitment to keep learning!
